          "text": "<h2 style=\"margin-left:0px;\">A Note From: Bridget Glynn-Baker</h2><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">Hi everyone,</span></p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">I’m very pleased to share Technology Business Management’s first all-hands of 2024.</span></p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">If you’re curious to learn more about what our TBM teams have been up to, I highly recommend watching the recording and/or looking through the deck on our </span><a href=\"https://technology.condenast.com/teams/technology-business-management\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>TBM team page</u></span></a><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">!</span></p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">In this session, we covered:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">TBM’s brand value story</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">Goals for 2024</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">Career &amp; Learning Updates</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">Q1 updates from Business Relationship Management, Technical Project</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">Management, Technology Marketing &amp; Engagement, and Solutions Management</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">Our China Strategy from a data and product solutions perspective from Jinhong Li</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">Have feedback? </span><a href=\"https://forms.gle/GhuL1Mci61xjpFb29\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Fill out this form here</u></span></a><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">. If you’d like to be invited to the next TBM all-hands, please reach out to </span><a href=\"mailto:faye.hirons@condenast.com\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Faye Hirons</u></span></a><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">Thanks,</span><br><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\">Bridget</span></p>",
